I2C Sensors:


Adafruit MCP9808 Precision I2C Temperature Sensor, $5, arduino code

Vdd--GND--SCL--SDA--ALert--A0--A1--A2



Adafruit HTU21D-F Temperature & Humidity Sensor Breakout Board, $15, arduino code

Vin--3v3--GND--SDA--SCL



AM2315 - Encased I2C Temperature/Humidity Sensor, $30, arduino code

Wired: 5V, GND, SCL, SDA



Adafruit BME280 Humidity + Barometric Pressure + Temperature Sensor Breakout, $20, arduino code

Vin--3V0--GND--SCK--SD0--SDI--CS
(SCK and SDI are the i2c logic pins)



SparkFun Humidity and Temperature Sensor Breakout - HIH6130, $30, arduino code
SCA--SCL--AL_L--AL_H--VDD--GND



DIGITAL SENSOR

DHT11 basic temperature-humidity sensor + extras, $5, arduino code
VDD--Data--Null--GND




